the Round Table.

04:35.442 --> 04:40.820
I wanted to follow
in his footsteps.

04:40.822 --> 04:43.613
By the fall of 2002
I had applied for a job

04:43.615 --> 04:45.699
at the United
Nations four times.

04:46.577 --> 04:47.409
Hey!

04:47.411 --> 04:48.536
Uncle Michael!

04:48.538 --> 04:49.495
My sister says it's
because Foreign Service

04:49.497 --> 04:50.704
