while interning at the U.N.

04:58.380 --> 04:59.921
So I got you
something small,

04:59.923 --> 05:01.966
but something else is
on it's way, okay?

05:01.968 --> 05:03.009
Hey, Trevor.

05:03.011 --> 05:04.093
Hey.

05:04.095 --> 05:05.719
Nice cake Lily,
got enough Danish flags?

05:05.721 --> 05:07.137
Yeah, yeah.

05:07.139 --> 05:09.514
Well, did you
hear anything?

05:09.516 --> 05:10.974
Uh, no.

05:10.976 --> 05:12.601
I'll hear tomorrow.

05:12.603 --> 05:14.603
But how'd it feel?

05:14.605 --> 05:15.855
Good?

05:15.857 --> 05:17.815
No, I was
too nervous.

05:17.817 --> 05:20.942
Oh well,
it's their loss.

05:20.944 --> 05:24.029
I'm sure you'll get it, you've
been working so hard for this!

05:24.031 --> 05:25.615
Yeah.

