going to present a problem.

14:59.190 --> 15:00.522
Okay.

15:00.524 --> 15:03.026
We can't let this
director sabotage the report.

15:03.028 --> 15:05.027
Why-why would he
sabotage his own report?

15:05.029 --> 15:06.653
She.

15:06.655 --> 15:08.739
So the Security Council will be
forced to lift the sanctions,

15:08.741 --> 15:11.993
and everybody can cash in on the
deals they made with Saddam back

15:11.995 --> 15:15.831
before he rolled into
Kuwait and pissed off the world.

15:16.541 --> 15:19.041
Jesus H. Christ, kid.

15:19.043 --> 15:21.045
Gonna have to fucking teach
you everything from scratch.

15:22.047 --> 15:26.965
Every six months we have to
justify our continued existence.

15:26.967 --> 15:30.636
Our job right now is to write a
report for the Security Council

15:30.638 --> 15:34.556
emphasizing all the good in
the Oil for Food program

15:34.558 --> 15:37.560
whilst minimizing
the challenges.

15:37.562 --> 15:39.145
Not to lie.

15:39.147 --> 15:41.064
No, never lie,

15:41.066 --> 15:47.820
but to choose our facts or
truths with the utmost care.

15:47.822 --> 15:48.988
Right.

15:52.369 --> 15:54.079
Can I trust you
to do that?

15:57.039 --> 15:59.250
Yes. Absolutely.

16:25.818 --> 16:27.068
There she is.

16:27.070 --> 16:28.945
Madame Dupre.

16:28.947 --> 16:30.990
