explain to her why she cannot

18:16.304 --> 18:20.055
have the stem cell
therapy that could cure her.

18:20.057 --> 18:23.392
Why she has to suffer because
the West begrudges Iraq,

18:23.394 --> 18:25.312
it's dignity.

18:30.359 --> 18:32.526
That I can't
explain, no.

18:45.250 --> 18:47.374
She asks
why you are crying?

18:59.180 --> 19:04.392
I promise I will do anything
I can to help your child.

19:20.660 --> 19:24.202
It sickens me to have to stand
there and listen to your lies.

19:24.204 --> 19:28.790
It's P.R., Christina, everyone
in the field is working so hard.

19:28.792 --> 19:30.500
Well, my reporter for
The Security Council

19:30.502 --> 19:32.504
is going to
tell the truth.

19:33.381 --> 19:34.632
Just so you know.

19:35.383 --> 19:37.093
Your report.

19:38.345 --> 19:41.094
The program
is a failure.

19:41.096 --> 19:42.138
The sanctions
aren't working.

19:42.140 --> 19:43.430
How is the
program failing?

19:43.432 --> 19:44.474
Medicine is
getting through!

19:44.476 --> 19:45.475
At what cost!?

19:45.477 --> 19:46.517
People are
getting basic staples.

19:46.519 --> 19:48.143
At what cost?

19:48.145 --> 19:50.438
Everybody is
grifting the system.

19:50.440 --> 19:52.230
Corruption grows
like a cancer.

19:52.232 --> 19:53.607
It'll never be
perfect and surely,

19:53.609 --> 19:56.736
it's better than
doing nothing.

19:56.738 --> 19:58.446
Michael,
what's the delay?

19:58.448 --> 20:00.448
Uhh, sorry, there's a
small security issue.

20:00.450 --> 20:02.824
We'll be on our way
in a few moments.

20:02.826 --> 20:05.702
I know
what you're doing.

20:05.704 --> 20:08.331
You want me to sign off
on your moral relativism

20:08.333 --> 20:11.417
so you can throw me under
the bus when it all unravels.

20:11.419 --> 20:13.251
You are mistaken.

20:13.253 --> 20:14.711
I'm just trying
to feed a country.

20:14.713 --> 20:16.756
Enough spin,
Costa, enough!

20:16.758 --> 20:18.507
The facts will
speak for themselves.

20:18.509 --> 20:20.301
My report with
The Security Council

20:20.303 --> 20:21.844
is going to
tell the truth.

20:53.961 --> 20:56.504
Baghdad is the centre
of the universe now, kid.

20:56.506 --> 20:59.673
