I have no idea.

51:29.755 --> 51:30.713
How would I...?

51:30.715 --> 51:34.300
Your boss,
what does he think?

51:34.302 --> 51:36.052
If you have
questions for Pasha,

51:36.054 --> 51:38.056
you should just
ask him yourself.

51:39.516 --> 51:45.353
Did he ever mention
anything about a list?

51:45.355 --> 51:47.315
